Let $A = (a_1, \ldots, a_n) \in D$, there exist open intervals $I_1, \ldots, I_n$ with $a_i \in I_i$ such that $I_1 \times \ldots \times I_n \subset D$ 
\par
I can set 
\[
f_i(t) = f(a_1, \ldots, a_{i-1}, t, a_{i+1}, \ldots, a_n) \qquad t \in I_i
\]